<plot>In honor of International Women's Year, CBC created this show which took the place of Luncheon Date in the noon slot each summer. With hosts, and often locations, alternated weekly, it covered a range of topics and guests from political figures to musicians. Prior to 1977, when Fred Latremouille and Guido Basso signed on, all hosts were female.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?521171</url></doc>
